  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nErigon version: `./erigon --version`\r\n\r\n```\r\nerigon version 2022.99.99-dev\r\ncommit 0cac29d1d2021562722dd6dec5d36f170d5a0a84 (HEAD -> devel, origin/devel, origin/HEAD)\r\nAuthor: Alex Sharov <AskAlexSharov@gmail.com>\r\nDate:   Sat Feb 26 19:55:17 2022 +0700\r\n```\r\n\r\nOS & Version: Windows/Linux/OSX\r\n\r\nLinux\r\n\r\nCommit hash : \r\n\r\ncommit 0cac29d1d2021562722dd6dec5d36f170d5a0a84 (HEAD -> devel, origin/devel, origin/HEAD)\r\nAuthor: Alex Sharov <AskAlexSharov@gmail.com>\r\nDate:   Sat Feb 26 19:55:17 2022 +0700\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\n\r\nAgreement with previous version of Erigon and current version of Nethermind when querying RPC\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\n\r\nDifference -- `eth_getBalance` appears to be off by one block\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\n\r\nBalance at block 0 against Nethermind:\r\n\r\n```\r\ncurl -s --data '{\"method\":\"eth_getBalance\",\"params\":[\"0x5abfec25f74cd88437631a7731906932776356f9\",\"0x0\"],\"id\":\"1\",\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\"}' -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -X POST <nethermind RPC>\r\n```\r\n\r\nReturns non-zero balance (correct):\r\n\r\n```\r\n{\r\n  \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\r\n  \"result\": \"0x9d83cc0dfa11177ff8000\",\r\n  \"id\": \"1\"\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nBalance at block 1 against Nethermind:\r\n\r\n\r\n```\r\ncurl -s --data '{\"method\":\"eth_getBalance\",\"params\":[\"0x5abfec25f74cd88437631a7731906932776356f9\",\"0x1\"],\"id\":\"1\",\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\"}' -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -X POST <nethermind RPC>\r\n```\r\n\r\nReturns non-zero balance (correct):\r\n\r\n```\r\n{\r\n  \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\r\n  \"result\": \"0x9d83cc0dfa11177ff8000\",\r\n  \"id\": \"1\"\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nBalance at block 0 against Erigon:\r\n\r\n```\r\ncurl -s --data '{\"method\":\"eth_getBalance\",\"params\":[\"0x5abfec25f74cd88437631a7731906932776356f9\",\"0x0\"],\"id\":\"1\",\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\"}' -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -X POST <erigon RPC>\r\n```\r\n\r\nReturns zero balance (**incorrect**):\r\n\r\n```\r\n{\r\n  \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\r\n  \"id\": \"1\",\r\n  \"result\": \"0x0\"\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nBalance at block 0 against Erigon:\r\n\r\n```\r\ncurl -s --data '{\"method\":\"eth_getBalance\",\"params\":[\"0x5abfec25f74cd88437631a7731906932776356f9\",\"0x1\"],\"id\":\"1\",\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\"}' -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -X POST <erigon RPC>\r\n```\r\n\r\nReturns non-zero balance (correct):\r\n\r\n```\r\n{\r\n  \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\r\n  \"id\": \"1\",\r\n  \"result\": \"0x9d83cc0dfa11177ff8000\"\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### Backtrace\r\n\r\n````\r\n[backtrace]\r\n````\r\n",
